{"tid":712166,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"網民網購手提電腦，遇到Windows啟用問題時客服竟教他直接破解了事！","createTime":"2018-06-22T02:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T08:08:20.000Z","uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a369a0fb09a360f75463310d66804d89a5b18bd","tid":712166,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:06:10.000Z","msg":"未啟用的《Windows 10》，普遍會在桌面右下角顯示「啟用 Windows」的水印，同時功能上也會受到一些限制。普遍市面有售的 Notebook，已經預載了正版《Windows 10》，毋須為啟用問題而煩惱。不過，有名為啊煎的支那網民，從神舟天貓旗艦店網購神舟（Hasee）戰神電競筆電後，向客戶服務員查詢該如何啟用《Windows 10》時，客服竟然教他使用翻版《Windows 10》常用的 KMS 啟用方式！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2095000/2096297/1036webchinanbkms01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2095000%2F2096297%2F1036webchinanbkms01_1024.jpg&h=e4e4176a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2096297/大陸網民網購神舟電腦！客服竟教他盜版%20Win%2010%20激活法\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2096297%2F%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC%E7%A5%9E%E8%88%9F%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%EF%BC%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%9C%8D%E7%AB%9F%E6%95%99%E4%BB%96%E7%9B%9C%E7%89%88%2520Win%252010%2520%E6%BF%80%E6%B4%BB%E6%B3%95&d=1e5ACuqD08pV3hsCkRtvsYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=e05f00b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2096297/大陸網民網購神舟電腦！客服竟教他盜版%20Win%2010%20激活法</a></div>"},{"pid":"773c7407889a5809326d41544b2bfb0fb80f24cd","tid":712166,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"神舟天貓旗艦店的客服回應啊煎的查詢時，竟指示他從百度雲中下載《Win 10 激活工具》，並從工具中點擊〈一鍵激活〉和〈自動續期〉來啟用《Windows 10》。該《Win 10 激活工具》雖然並非常用來啟用盜版《Windows 10》的《KMSpico》，但亦提供了類似的功能，可利用到 KMS 大量啟用授權的方式，讓翻版《Windows 10》激活成為正版。由於較早期的 KMS《Windows 10》啟用工具，會在啟用時出現「跑馬仔」的動畫，故此「跑馬仔」也成為了使用 KMS 破解盜版《Windows 10》啟用限制的別稱。<br />\n<br />\n不過，另一名神舟天貓旗艦店客服，則表示只要先不要上網，再關閉系統更新和開啟獨立顯示卡，再連接 Wi-Fi 或有線網絡上網，即可自動完成《Windows 10》啟用程序。"},{"pid":"1bce2252b35b1a3ceac18acaabe728be83332eb8","tid":712166,"uid":37796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:22:58.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"4d4a1cca29ecde8bd5394f6b1ff97fe610650cb3","tid":712166,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"用ROUTER做破解仲方便, KMS都唔洗裝, 真接可以UPDATE, OFFICE都無問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc20f24e1f486d6a00ac81daf627432af34cea5","tid":712166,"uid":4120,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"在的呢😝"},{"pid":"2a9411ea8fbd5480020a21fa96e841f99984f2d5","tid":712166,"uid":40119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc20f24e1f486d6a00ac81daf627432af34cea5","tid":712166,"uid":4120,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"在的呢😝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ddc140c42d84b4676f948c1efa90a73529faf6","tid":712166,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">蚹蛤蚑那蟈蜻</span></span>"},{"pid":"83a32923ffff4acfa482410e9ba8976691cf5a0b","tid":712166,"uid":80565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d4a1cca29ecde8bd5394f6b1ff97fe610650cb3","tid":712166,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"用ROUTER做破解仲方便, KMS都唔洗裝, 真接可以UPDATE, OFFICE都無問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:08:20.000Z","msg":"點樣用router破解"}]}